            <div class="J_Content" data-emote="3">
                <!---doc_text---><p align="center" style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:center;"><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">-2008</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">月时事</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"></span></b>
<p align="center" style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:center;"><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">8</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">月时事政治</span></b><span style="font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p align="left" style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">&nbsp; </font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">一、国内部分：</span></b><span style="font-family:&#718;"></span>
<ol type="1">
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">29</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">30</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">分许，河南省陕县支建矿业有限公司支建煤矿东风井发生透水事故，造成</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">69</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人被困，经及时抢救全部生还。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，国家主席胡锦涛在北京人民大会堂会见美国总统特别代表、财政部长保尔森。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">《行政复议条例》</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日施行，政府强化</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">自我纠错</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，中共中央总书记、国家主席、中央军委主席胡锦涛在庆祝中国人民解放军建军</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">80</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">周年暨全军英雄模范代表大会上发表重要讲话。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华网北京</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日电，中国外交部发言人刘建超</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日表示，台湾当局申请</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">以台湾名义加入联合国</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的举动是荒谬的。是企图把台湾从中国分割出去的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">台独</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">分裂行径。我们对此坚决反对并密切关注事态发展。台湾当局这一分裂中国的图谋绝不可能得逞。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华网北京８月４日电，国务院总理温家宝在北京市农产品市场考察时强调，保持价格总水平基本稳定关系全局。各地区、各部门必须切实负起责任，加强领导，做好主要食品生产、供应和价格稳定工作，为迎接党的十七大胜利召开创造良好的环境。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华社北京８月５日电，国家食品药品监督管理局副局长惠鲁生近日在接受新华社记者采访时表示，当前食品安全形势有所好转，但仍然严峻。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">据国家发展和改革委员会６日介绍，发展改革委办公厅日前发出通知，要求各地将开展食品价格及相关收费专项检查作为当前的一项政治任务，严肃查处价格串通、哄抬价格、价格欺诈等三类不正当价格行为。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">自５月份全国猪肉涨价以来，少数不法商贩借机私屠滥宰、制售注水肉和病害猪肉，严重损害了消费者的合法权益，威胁到人民群众的身体健康。国家工商行政管理总局６日发出紧急通知，要求各省市工商、发展改革委、公安、农业、商务、卫生、食品药品主管部门，采取切实措施进一步加强猪肉市场管理。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华社北京８月８日电，中央等电贺内蒙古自治区成立</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">60</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">周年。曾庆红率中央代表团参加内蒙古</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">60</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">周年庆祝活动。中央赠</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">民族团结宝鼎</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，北京</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2008</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年奥运会倒计时一周年庆祝活动在天安门广场举行。中共中央政治局常委、全国人大常委会委员长吴邦国出席庆祝活动并讲话。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">据国家统计局网站消息，</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月全国居民消费价格上涨</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">5.6%&nbsp;</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">肉禽制品涨</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">45.2%</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1-7</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月份累计，居民消费价格总水平同比上涨</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">3.5%</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。　</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华网北京８月９日电，农业部有关负责人９日说，</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">22</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">省份出现旱情农业部紧急部署抗旱工作。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华网北京</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">13</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日电，新华社受权发布《国务院关于解决城市低收入家庭住房困难的若干意见》。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">８月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">13</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">16</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">45</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">分许，湖南省湘西自治州凤凰县沱江大桥发生坍塌事故，造成人员严重伤亡。胡锦涛总书记在国外访问期间就湖南省凤凰县沱江大桥坍塌事故作出重要指示。要求尽最大努力搜救下落不明人员和救治伤员。目前已确认有</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">64</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人在这场灾难中不幸罹难，</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">88</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人脱险，其中</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">22</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人受伤。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">国务院</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">13</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日晚发出紧急通知，要求各地区、各部门进一步落实促进生猪等副食品生产供应的各项政策措施，保证市场供应，维护副食品价格稳定。通知说，近期我国居民消费价格总水平出现明显上涨，社会各方面普遍关注，已成为当前宏观经济运行的突出问题。带动价格总水平上涨的主要是粮食、猪肉等，这与当前国际市场粮油及初级产品价格上涨、生产成本增加等密切相关，但也存在少数经营者趁机合谋涨价、哄抬价格等现象，扰乱了正常的市场秩序，损害了群众利益。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华网北京８月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日电，为了全面加强综合减灾能力建设，提高防范应对自然灾害能力，保障人民群众生命财产安全，促进经济社会全面协调可持续发展，国务院办公厅近日印发《国家综合减灾</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">十一五</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">规划》。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">国务院决定自</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日起，将储蓄存款利息所得个人所得税的适用税率由现行的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">％调减为</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">％。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，国家广电总局向各省、自治区、直辖市广播影视局，新疆生产建设兵团广播电视局、中央三台、中国教育电视台下发通报，批评重庆电视台举办播出的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">第一次心动</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">选拔活动严重违规行为。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日夜间开始，山东新汶突降暴雨，山洪暴发，导致柴汶河东都河堤被冲垮。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时洪水涌入华源煤矿。截至</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">18</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时，华源煤矿</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">172</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人下落不明。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时，同样原因导致新泰市名公煤矿</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">9</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人被困矿井下。事故发生后，胡锦涛温家宝指示，要求全力救援。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">国务院新闻办公室</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日发表了《中国的食品质量安全状况》白皮书，从食品生产和质量概况、食品监管体制和监管工作、进出口食品的监管等方面对中国食品质量安全状况作了介绍和说明。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">19</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，中国与尼日尔恢复外交关系。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">19</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">分左右，山东魏桥创业集团所属铝母铸造分厂发生铝水外溢事故。截至</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时，事故死亡人数已上升至</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人，伤者</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">59</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">人。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华社北京８月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日电，截至</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">20</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">17</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">时的统计，第９号台风</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">圣帕</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">已造成福建、浙江、江西三省２０人死亡，直接经济损失逾</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">24</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">亿元。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华社北京８月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">21</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日电，中国武警部队将于９月上旬赴俄罗斯，在莫斯科与俄罗斯内卫部队举行代号为</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
