  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">国际原子能机构与伊朗</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">21</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日就旨在解决伊朗核计划中悬而未决问题的行动计划达成协议。伊朗</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
