  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">日本海上自卫队最大型护卫舰</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
