  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">参选人谢长廷、苏贞昌提名造势，同时也将讨论争议多时的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">正常国家决议文</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
