  face="Times New Roman">58</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">周年，胡锦涛、吴邦国、贾庆林、曾庆红、吴官正、李长春、罗干等出席，温家宝发表讲话。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
