face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">年</span></b><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">10</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">月时事政治</span></b><span style="font-family:&#718;"></span>
<p align="left" style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><b><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
face="Times New Roman">&nbsp; </font></span></b><b><span style="font-family:宋体;">一、国内部分：</span></b><span style="font-family:&#718;"></span>
<ol type="1">
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，《预包装饮料酒标签通则》已正式实施，但昨日记者走访部分超市发现，劝酒警示语仍然难得一见。据有关部门介绍，执行不力的企业或受到警告。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，中国国家大剧院上周进行了首次试演。美国《今日美国》报评论认为，国家大剧院的落成象征了中国强大的经济实力，并将吸引国际文化产业投资。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，中国海军已经拥有现代化武器装备仿真试验场。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">02</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，胡锦涛主席同冰岛总统格里姆松会谈。胡锦涛主席会见菲律宾总统阿罗约。胡锦涛主席会见国际特殊奥林匹克委员会主席施莱佛。胡锦涛主席宴请出席２００７年世界夏季特奥会开幕式的国际贵宾。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">新华社北京１０月３日电，随着３８家单位近日被批准为</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">国家水利风景区</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，中国国家水利风景区达到２７２家。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">03</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">2007</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年世界夏季特殊奥林匹克运动会在上海隆重开幕，胡锦涛出席开幕式并宣布运动会开幕，本届运动会将于</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日闭幕。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">03</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，智障人士福利全球政策高峰论坛在上海举行。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">03</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，六方会谈制定《落实共同声明第二阶段行动》共同文件。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">04</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日上午，特奥会半程马拉松比赛男子组决赛在上海新江湾城举行，南非特奥运动员尼尔森</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">"</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">杰姆斯</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">"</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">巴斯以</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">小时</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">26</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">分</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">26</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">秒的成绩获得了本届特奥会的首枚金牌。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，记者从中央气象台获悉，今年第</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">16</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">号强台风</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">罗莎</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">于</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日凌晨加强为超强台风，由今年第</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">15</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">号热带风暴</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">利奇马</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">减弱成的热带低压已于</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日晚上停止编号。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">１０月６日，卫生部部长陈竺日前在２００７年全国疾控中心主任年会上强调指出，疾病预防控制工作是中国卫生工作的第一关口。我国当前的卫生工作必须</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">关口前移</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，预防为主。财政部副部长王军近日表示：国家财政支出用于社会保障的比例，已经从一九九八年的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">5.52%</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">提高到二</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">○○</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">六年的</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">11.5%</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">国家安全生产监督管理总局局长李毅中８日强调，在安全生产隐患排查治理专项行动中发现的所有重大隐患，都要逐条做到治理责任、措施、资金、期限和应急预案</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">五落实</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">联合国教科文组织官员理查德</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">．</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">恩哥哈特８日在丽江宣布，世界文化遗产丽江古城遗产保护民居修复项目荣获</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">联合国教科文组织亚太地区２００７年遗产保护优秀奖</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">１０月８日，来自中共中央组织部公布的全国党内统计最新数据显示，截至２００７年６月，全国中共党员总数为７３３６．３万名，比２００２年党的十六大时增加６４２．２万名。全国现有党的基层组织３６０．７万个，比２００２年党的十六大时增加１４．２万个。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">中共十六届七中全会于２００７年１０月９日在北京召开。中共中央政治局将向中共十六届七中全会建议，中国共产党第十七次全国代表大会于２００７年１０月１５日在北京召开。这次会议还审议了中央纪委向中共十七大的工作报告稿，同意将这一工作报告稿提交中共十六届七中全会讨论。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，有媒体报道称，国家将调整休假制度，取消</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">五一</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">黄金周，将传统节日定为法定假日。对此，国家旅游局新闻处未予否认，但表示国务院已委托国家发改委调研假日调整方案，最终方案将等待人大批准通过后实施。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:宋体;">１０月８日，以科学发展为主题的对策性研究机构</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">——</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">成都科学发展研究院８日正式挂牌成立。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">9</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，一些专家认为，近</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">30</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年来，党对科学社会主义基本原则的认识，经历了三次重大的转变：第一次重大转变：从计划到市场。第二次重大转变：从手段到目的。第三次重大转变：从经济到全面。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman"> </font></span>
  <li style="line-height:19.5pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;text-align:left;"><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日，值得关注的八个理论关键词。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">“</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">解放思想</span><span style="font-family:&#718;"><font
  face="Times New Roman">”</font></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family:&#718;">